yubikey-luks (0.5.1-2) trusty; urgency=low

  * Rewritten in bash
  * Added lots of error checking
  * Added function to determine root disk instead of hard-coding sda
  * Added check for key slot before going further
  * Changed all flag checks to numbers
  * Added strict mode.

